summary: Experienced English Language Teacher and Educational Director with a demonstrated history of working in the education and education management industry. Skilled in English-TurkishTranslation, English as a Second Language Materials Development, Teaching and Teacher Training. Volunteer work in Non-Governmental Organizations (NGOs). Strong business development professional with a Master of Arts focused in English Language Teaching and Education from Eastern Mediterranean University.
